data.description: Look no further! This beautiful Custom traditional home has Everything! It features 3-sided brick finish, 5-bedrooms, 5- full bathrooms, 3 stunning fireplaces intricately finished with detailed mantles, Luxurious Master on the main floor, complete with a full separate sitting area with a fireplace for ambiance, huge master bathroom has every feature you could wish for, including a double sized walk-in closet and there is also a second master suite on the second level. The kitchen has custom cabinets with granite counter tops and a large island with a 4 seat eat at bar and full eat-in breakfast area all finished with gorgeous crown molding and open to the great room with cathedral ceilings. The basement is finished with very high ceilings, a second kitchen, a large living room, an in home gym and an amazing fully equipped theater room, including projector and built in speaker system. What more could you ask for? Move right in and make yourself at home! This amazing find is on the cul-de-sac in an ideal location and is meticulously maintained including a new roof, new A/C and recently serviced septic tank--no detail left unattended. Hurry out and take a look, this property will not last long!  Home is unavailable for showings.
